      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 134: 🔴 Critical Issues: Edition body overrides are matched by edition vector index (`bodyOverwrite_e0`, `bodyOverwrite_e1`, ...). If the daemon changes edition ordering, inserts missing editions, or returns a subset, plugin data can be applied to the wrong historical message body. Key the plugin data by the stable edition id instead of positional index, or preserve an explicit daemon-provided mapping. Example:\n```suggestion\nconst auto pdKey \u003d QString(\"bodyOverwrite_%1\").arg(edition.value(\"id\"));\nconst auto pdIt \u003d msg.pluginData.find(pdKey);\n```",
